dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"沙夏在《Financial Times》的足球商業高峰會解釋：「如我之前所說，我覺得單膝下跪已經開始失去價值。<span class=\"red\"><strong>從小父母教育我，我應該為身為黑人而自豪，不論如何，我覺得我們應該堅挺站著。</strong></span>也因為現在單膝下跪，我們在賽前做，有時有些人甚至已經忘記了。想想背後的意義，如果只是為做而做，我覺得並不足夠，我不會再單膝下跪，也不會穿Black Lives Matter在我衫的背後，因為那像一個目標。我們正孤立自己，我們嘗試說人人平等，但在這些東西上我們正在孤立自己，而且收不到成效，因此這是我的立場。」他也強調「除非有實際行動，否則不用再跟他談這些」。早前英冠球隊賓福特也叫停了這個儀式。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=9edf700c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"861ae410562c585551b700280df47b6aa6f01065","tid":2445412,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"人地之前已經講明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf4287e9389ab2389e319a01c7860a019000103","tid":2445412,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:15:33.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd552e528e44c50c1b49feeebab021ffa00d9a0","tid":2445412,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:15:36.000Z","msg":"You ain&rsquo;t black<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dcf5fb8b3c182e755b359e4a877d50c0c01eede","tid":2445412,"uid":997,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:15:42.000Z","msg":"Zaha睇得咁透, 呢個世界真係要整條虛偽罪去懲罰班虛偽撚/左膠"},{"pid":"f567ef56a27b61d0f33f207f742cdee09e6b92c4","tid":2445412,"uid":294121,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"respect<br />\n黑人自尊心不嬲好強<br />\n俾班blm搞到黑人好似廢到變受保護動物咁"},{"pid":"dc6fb42fe9ee2ffa0643084479898c9a24bf924b","tid":2445412,"uid":244797,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"f567ef56a27b61d0f33f207f742cdee09e6b92c4","tid":2445412,"uid":294121,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"cit